 6. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the photographer##1
 7. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
 8. the dressmaker is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the project-manager##1
10. the person driving the train is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
